  "instructions": [
    "Slice the kielbasa into thin strips and set aside.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens, diced cucumber, mango, and almonds.",
    "Whisk together the lime juice, fish sauce, tamarind paste, olive oil, and chili flakes to create the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently to coat.",
    "Add the sliced kielbasa and sprinkle with fresh mint, cilantro, and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Gently mix everything together so the flavors meld.",
    "Serve immediately on a chilled plate, garnishing with extra herbs if desired."
